title: [Vornavian Coast, Foggy Valley]
description: Columns of trees guide the path straight to the west, but the tops of stubborn bushes poke above the fog, defining the path to the southeast.  The tops of the trees above provide a complete canopy, blocking out all moonlight and giving the fog an eerie greenish glow.
